---
import Container from '../ui/Container.astro'
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-dark py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24">

  <Container class="relative z-10">
    <div class="cta-content mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      {/* Badge */}
      <div class="mb-6 text-center">
        <span class="inline-block rounded-full border border-lime/30 bg-lime/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-display font-bold text-lime backdrop-blur-sm">
          PRÓXIMO PASSO
        </span>
      </div>

      {/* Headline */}
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-center font-display text-display-sm tracking-tight text-white md:text-display-md">
        Comece Pelo <span class="text-lime">Diagnóstico Gratuito</span>
      </h2>

      {/* Subheadline */}
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-center font-sans text-body-lg text-gray-200">
        Descubra qual dos 6Ps está travando seu crescimento. Leva 10 minutos e você recebe o resultado na hora.
      </p>

      {/* Benefícios em lista */}
      <div class="mx-auto mb-10 grid max-w-2xl gap-4 text-left md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/50 p-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-lime/20">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-lime" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-white">10 minutos, resultado imediato</p>
            <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-sm text-gray-400">Sem enrolação, direto ao ponto</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/50 p-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-lime/20">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-lime" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-white">Identifica o gargalo real</p>
            <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-sm text-gray-400">Para de chutar o que fazer</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/50 p-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-lime/20">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-lime" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-white">Baseado em 140+ diagnósticos</p>
            <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-sm text-gray-400">Testado em vários nichos e portes</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/50 p-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-lime/20">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-lime" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-white">Completamente gratuito</p>
            <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-sm text-gray-400">Sem cartão, sem pegadinha</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* CTAs */}
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="/diagnostico" data-astro-prefetch>
          <button class="inline-flex h-14 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-lime px-8 font-display text-lg font-bold text-dark shadow-lg shadow-lime/20 transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:bg-lime/90 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-lime focus:ring-offset-2 sm:w-auto">
            <span>Fazer Diagnóstico Agora</span>
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </a>
        <a href="/vendas-sem-segredos" data-astro-prefetch>
          <button class="inline-flex h-14 w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-white px-8 font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:bg-white/10 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:ring-offset-2 sm:w-auto">
            Ou Conhecer o Vendas Sem Segredos
          </button>
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* Micro-copy */}
      <p class="mt-6 text-center font-sans text-sm text-gray-400">
        Já fiz centenas de diagnósticos. 9 em cada 10 descobrem que o problema não é onde achavam. Bora descobrir?
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-content {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
